companyName: 1st Federal Savings Bank of SC, Inc.
description: 1st Federal Savings Bank of SC, Inc. provides various banking products and services. It offers personal and business checking, savings, and individual retirement accounts, as well as certificates of deposit; check reorder, debit card, overdraft protection, automated telephone teller, wire transfer, night deposit drop, safe deposit box, direct deposit, and automatic transfer services; and online banking services. The company also provides mortgage, consumer, and commercial loans; and Kasasa products. 1st Federal Savings Bank of SC, Inc. was founded in 1962 and is based in Walterboro, South Carolina.
